# Ramadan Tracker — project overview

**Flutter** offline-first Ramadan and sunnah habit tracker. Package: `ramadan_tracker`.

## Stack

- **State:** Riverpod — `lib/data/providers/`
- **DB:** Drift/SQLite — `lib/data/database/`
- **Charts:** fl_chart — insights tabs
- **Widget:** home_widget — Android sunnah summary
- **Entry:** `lib/main.dart` → `lib/app/`

## App structure

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| Today / fasting | `lib/features/today/` |
| Month calendar | `lib/features/month/` |
| Autopilot plan | `lib/features/plan/` |
| Sunnah fasting | `lib/features/sunnah/` |
| Zakat / Fidyah / Qadha | `lib/features/qadha/` |
| Insights | `lib/features/insights/` |
| Settings / onboarding | `lib/features/settings/`, `onboarding/` |
| l10n | `lib/l10n/` (EN + ID) |

## Dev commands

```bash
flutter pub get
flutter pub run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs   # after schema changes
flutter test
flutter analyze
flutter run
```

